print "hello world!"
print "shutting down now. Farewell oh cruel, cruel world!"
</pre>
  
接著，編輯<code>packages/pyhelloworld/files/README.txt</code> 寫入以下的說明：

  This is the most awesome helloworld application ever. Know why? It has SNAKES!

